div.p:
This icon is named "linkedin" and is licensed under the open source "MIT License" license. It's a colored icon. It's available to be downloaded in SVG and PNG formats (available in 256, 512, 1024 and 2048 PNG sizes).
It's part of the icon set "Super Tiny Icons", which has 281 icons in it.
This graphic is also a logo. It's useful if you want to show the logo (for branding purposes) on your website or app.
If you need this icon available in another format, it should be pretty straight forward to download it as an SVG image file, and then import it into apps like Figma, Sketch, Snappa or Visme. Converting it to an ICO, JPEG or WebP image format or file type should also be pretty simple (we hope to add that feature to Iconduck soon).
This icon can be used for both Personal & Commercial purposes and projects, but please check the license to see if the designer is requesting attribution (for example, a link back to their website).
It was added to Iconduck on: 31 December, 2020
Some use-cases for this icon include:

ul.li: Using as a button on your website
Pinning to a Pinterest photo or image
Including in a header for your website or blog
Using in a Google Slides presentation

div.p: Related tags: professional, logos, linkedin, brands, social media

div.h3: Can I use this icon for personal purposes/projects?
div.p: Yes. This icon can be freely used for personal projects including websites, designs, presentations and other things.
div.h3: Can I use this icon for commercial purposes/projects?
div.p: Yes. This icon can be used for commercial purposes, but may require attribution (eg. a link). If it's a logo or trademark, it may be owned by another company.
div.h3: Can I download this icon for free?
div.p: Yes! This icon has been open sourced, and can be downloaded at no charge / for free. We also don't require you to sign up for Iconduck, but you can join our mailing list to get notifications on when new icons are available.
div.h3: Where can I find free branding icons & illustrations?
div.p: Iconduck has 118,894 free open source icons & illustrations. You can find more branding icons right on this website.
